text:
Hello all,

A silly poll is about to happen but necessary. And I’m so thankful you guys are so active!! I called Flying Biscuit early this morning and they do not take reservations. Last I went the place was kind of small, we could probably take over their whole establishment. So three ideas:

:one: we go at 8:00AM when they open
:two: we go at 12:00PM as stated, try our luck or grab pick up and go to park
:three: we go at 12:00PM, as stated, see if FB have tables and if not go to Shake Shack
:v: You make the call and I’ll be fine with whatever you choose.

I’ll update you with final decisions at 7:00PM EST.
Location: 12th street gate at piedmont park (<https://goo.gl/maps/H4RF4s3KBDrwsNvBA>)

Hope this helps!
Cherie Lum
